<script type="text/javascript" src="/smoothie.js"></script>
   
   
 
<canvas id="network-timeline" width="288" height= "100" style="margin-bottom:15px"></canvas>



<script>

(function(scope) {
  var timer = setInterval(function() { //check that the Morris libs are loaded, if not wait
  var ch1 = new SmoothieChart();
  if (!ch1) return;
  clearInterval(timer);
 
 
       var t1 = new TimeSeries();
       var t2 = new TimeSeries();
        var t3 = new TimeSeries();
         var t4 = new TimeSeries();
        var chart = new SmoothieChart({millisPerPixel:87,scaleSmoothing:0.292,grid:{fillStyle:'#2A3F54',millisPerLine:1000},labels:{disabled:false,showIntermediateLabels:true},maxValue:100,minValue:-10});
        chart.addTimeSeries(t1, { strokeStyle: 'rgba(51,255,255,1)', fillStyle: 'rgba(51,255,255,0.2)', lineWidth: 1.5 });
        chart.addTimeSeries(t2, { strokeStyle: 'rgba(153,0,255, 1)', fillStyle: 'rgba(153,0,255, 0.2)', lineWidth: 1.5 });
        chart.addTimeSeries(t3, { strokeStyle: 'rgba(153,255,102,1)', fillStyle: 'rgba(153,255,102, 0.2)', lineWidth: 1.5 });
        chart.addTimeSeries(t4, { strokeStyle: 'rgba(255,255,51, 1)', fillStyle: 'rgba(255,255,51, 0.2)', lineWidth: 1.5 });


        chart.streamTo(document.getElementById("network-timeline"), 1000);
   // setInterval(function() {
         
          t1.append(Date.now(), 0.0);
          t2.append(Date.now(), 0.0);
          t3.append(Date.now(), 0.0);
          t4.append(Date.now(), 0.0);
     //  }, 3000);
    var timer2 = setInterval(function() {
      chart.stop();
        clearInterval(timer2);
      }, 2000);
    
     //alert(scope);
 
 scope.$watch('msg', function (msg) { //watch for an incoming NR msg
 if (msg) {
  chart.start();
  if (msg.payload == 'STOP') {
      chart.stop();
      return;
  }
 t1.append(Date.now(), msg.NETR[0]);
 t2.append(Date.now(), msg.NETR[1]);
 t3.append(Date.now(), msg.NETW[0]);
 t4.append(Date.now(), msg.NETW[1]);
 
 
  
 };
 }); //close out the watch 
  }, 100); // close out the setInterval 
})(scope);


</script>

format:
<script type="text/javascript" src="/smoothie.js"></script>
   
   
 
<canvas id="network-timeline" width="288" height= "100" style="margin-bottom:15px"></canvas>



<script>

(function(scope) {
  var timer = setInterval(function() { //check that the Morris libs are loaded, if not wait
  var ch1 = new SmoothieChart();
  if (!ch1) return;
  clearInterval(timer);
 
 
       var t1 = new TimeSeries();
       var t2 = new TimeSeries();
        var t3 = new TimeSeries();
         var t4 = new TimeSeries();
        var chart = new SmoothieChart({millisPerPixel:87,scaleSmoothing:0.292,grid:{fillStyle:'#2A3F54',millisPerLine:1000},labels:{disabled:false,showIntermediateLabels:true},maxValue:100,minValue:-10});
        chart.addTimeSeries(t1, { strokeStyle: 'rgba(51,255,255,1)', fillStyle: 'rgba(51,255,255,0.2)', lineWidth: 1.5 });
        chart.addTimeSeries(t2, { strokeStyle: 'rgba(153,0,255, 1)', fillStyle: 'rgba(153,0,255, 0.2)', lineWidth: 1.5 });
        chart.addTimeSeries(t3, { strokeStyle: 'rgba(153,255,102,1)', fillStyle: 'rgba(153,255,102, 0.2)', lineWidth: 1.5 });
        chart.addTimeSeries(t4, { strokeStyle: 'rgba(255,255,51, 1)', fillStyle: 'rgba(255,255,51, 0.2)', lineWidth: 1.5 });


        chart.streamTo(document.getElementById("network-timeline"), 1000);
   // setInterval(function() {
         
          t1.append(Date.now(), 0.0);
          t2.append(Date.now(), 0.0);
          t3.append(Date.now(), 0.0);
          t4.append(Date.now(), 0.0);
     //  }, 3000);
    var timer2 = setInterval(function() {
      chart.stop();
        clearInterval(timer2);
      }, 2000);
    
     //alert(scope);
 
 scope.$watch('msg', function (msg) { //watch for an incoming NR msg
 if (msg) {
  chart.start();
  if (msg.payload == 'STOP') {
      chart.stop();
      return;
  }
 t1.append(Date.now(), msg.monitor.List[0].BytesReceivedTotal/1024);
 t2.append(Date.now(), msg.monitor.List[1].BytesReceivedTotal/1024);
 t3.append(Date.now(), msg.monitor.List[0].BytesSentTotal/1024);
 t4.append(Date.now(), msg.monitor.List[1].BytesSentTotal/1024);
 
 
  
 };
 }); //close out the watch 
  }, 100); // close out the setInterval 
})(scope);


</script>
